steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitmodulesms006user" and Comment "Testing Module for SMS - User"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitmodulesms006user" display
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I add module "SMS login with Twilio"
When I select multi dropdown has label "Associated users tables" with value "jitmodulesms006users"
When I press Save button popover popup
Then I should see the warning popup with message "SMS login with Twilio module added successfully"
Then I should see module "SMS login with Twilio" was added by Edit button
When I edit module "SMS login with Twilio"
Then I should see item "jitmodulesms006users" was selected for multi dropdown with label "Associated users tables"
Then I should see texbox no headder with label "OTP code length" has value "4"
Then I should see Header "Production" is collapsed
Then I should see Header "Staging" is collapsed
Then I should see Header "Development" is collapsed
When I close the popover popup
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I delete without verification the table with Name "jitmodulesms006user"
Then I should see the warning popup with message "Cannot delete this table because this table is associated to some modules"
When I press "No" button modal popup
When I navigate to menu "Modules" without submenu
Then I should see Modules screen display
When I reset module "SMS login with Twilio"
Then I should NOT see module "SMS login with Twilio" was added by Edit button
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I delete the table with Name "jitmodulesms006user"
Then I should NOT see the table with Name "jitmodulesms006user" display
